name: Tetra cylinder
formula:
[advanced]

public IneqMesh GetIneqMesh()
{
    return new IneqMesh
    {
      X0 = -0.75,
      Y0 = -0.75,
      Z0 = -0.75,
      X1 = 2.25,
      Y1 = 2.25,
      Z1 = 2.25,
      D = 0.1d,
      Boxed = false,
      IneqTree =
        IneqLib.Ball(0, 0, 0, 0.55) |
        IneqLib.Ball(1.5, 0, 0, 0.55) |
        IneqLib.Ball(0.75, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3), 0, 0.55) |
        IneqLib.Ball(2.25 / 3, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, Math.Sqrt(2.25 - Math.Pow(2 * 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, 2)), 0.55) |

        IneqLib.Cylinder(0, 0, 0, 1.5, 0, 0, 0.2, 1.5) |
        IneqLib.Cylinder(0, 0, 0, 0.75, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3), 0, 0.2, 1.5) |
        IneqLib.Cylinder(0, 0, 0, 2.25 / 3, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, Math.Sqrt(2.25 - Math.Pow(2 * 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, 2)), 0.2, 1.5) |

        IneqLib.Cylinder(1.5, 0, 0, 0.75, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3), 0, 0.2, 1.5) |
        IneqLib.Cylinder(1.5, 0, 0, 2.25 / 3, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, Math.Sqrt(2.25 - Math.Pow(2 * 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, 2)), 0.2, 1.5) |

        IneqLib.Cylinder(0.75, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3), 0, 2.25 / 3, 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, Math.Sqrt(2.25 - Math.Pow(2 * 1.5 * Math.Sin(2 * Math.PI / 3) / 3, 2)), 0.2, 1.5)
      };
}
